quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,Mu vy’ukuri ikiremwa muntu carahitiwe n’umwanya muremure w’imyaka myinshi kita raba ikintu na kimwe kivurwa kuri we
  76,2,"Mu vy’ukuri twaremye umuntu biturutse kumbuto y’ubuzima ivanzwe ni y’umugabo hamwe ni y’umugore, kugira ngo tumugirire ibibazo, kuri ivyo tumugira uwumva n’ukubona"
  76,3,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twara murongoye mu nzira zose azoba arimwo aba uwushima canke uwuhakana
  76,4,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaraba teguriye abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, iminyororo hamwe n’imigozi y’umuriro ukaze cane"
  76,5,Mu vy’ukuri abantu beranda bazonywa ibinyobwa bivanzwe mwo n’akamoto kitiriwe Kafuri
  76,6,"Iyo\tKafuri\tn’umwonga\tuzonywa\tmwo\tabantu\tberanda\tb’Imana\tukazo shunguruka mwo amazi afise ishunguruka ryiza nkuko bipfuza"
  76,7,Abo bantu ni bamwe bakwijije ibikenewe vyabo n’ugutinya umusi w’ishari ryawo uzo kwiragira hose
  76,8,"Naba gaburira ibi fungurwa aboro hamwe n’impfuvyi hamwe n’imbohe, mugihe nabo ku bwabo bakunda ivyo bifungurwa"
  76,9,"Mu mitima yabo bavuga bati:- tuba risha ibi bifungurwa kugushaka impuhwe z’Imana gusa, kuko ntidushaka kuri mwebwe impembo iyariyo yose canke yuko mwodushimira"
  76,10,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe dutinya ku Muremyi wacu uwo musi w’ingorane n’uburuhe
  76,11,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tImana\tizoba\tkingira\tn’ishari\tryuwo\tmusi\tn’ukuba\thuza n’imigisha yayo hamwe n’akanya muneza ntangere"
  76,12,"Imana\tizo\tbaha\takaganuke\tk’imirima\tyo\tmw’ijuru\thamwe\tn’impuzu zihwahutse kubera ukwigumya kwabo"
  76,13,"Iyo mw’ijuru bazo kwegamira kunyegamo z’iteka, nti bazobona yo izuba rikaze cane , canke imbeho ikaze cane kuribo"
  76,14,"N’ibitutu\tvyayo\tbizoba\tbiri\thafi\tcane\tkuri\tbo,\thamwe\tn’ivyamwa vyegeranye kubindi bishunguruka bigerekeranye kubindi kugera hasi"
  76,15,Bazo cishirizwa ibikoresho vy’umwakaka hamwe n’ibikombe bibonerana
  76,16,N’ibirahuri vy’umwakaka vyujujwe kurugero rumwe rukwiye
  76,17,"Iyo\tmw’ijuru\tbazonyweshwa\tibinyobwa\tbivanzwe\tmwo\tn’ikirungo citiriwe Tangawizi"
  76,18,Urwo n’uruzi ruri mw’ijuru rwitiriwe Sal’sabila
  76,19,"Bazo kikuzwa n’imisore isharije, ubabonye womengo n’ubutare bwitiriwe Ilulu za sanzajwe"
  76,20,"Ubonye ibirimwo, uzoca ubona imigisha hamwe n’ubwami bw’Imana bunini cane"
  76,21,"Hejuru yabo barafise impuzu zihwahutse z’ibara ry’urwatsi rubisi, hamwe n’izindi zihwahutse ziremereye gatoyi, kandi bazokwambikwa ingori z’umwakaka, n’Umuremyi wabo azoba nywesha ibinyobwa vyiza cane"
  76,22,Mu vy’ukuri iyi niyo mpembo yanyu yibijanye n’ibikorwa vyanyu vyemewe
  76,23,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twakumanuriye iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ibice bice
  76,24,"Rero n’urindire intahe y’Umuremyi wawe, kandi ntugamburukire umwe muribo mubagira ibicumuro canke uwuhakana Imana yiwe y’ukuri"
  76,25,Ni wibuke izina ry’Umuremyi wawe mu gitondo no ku mugoroba
  76,26,"Mw’ijoro naho uyunamire ushize umutwe wawe hasi, kandi uyi ninahaze mw’ijoro mumwanya muremure"
  76,27,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\taba\tbantu\tbikundira\tubuzima\tbwo\tngaha\tkw’Isi\tgusa, n’ugusiga inyuma yabo umusi ugoye cane kuribo"
  76,28,"Twebwe twabaremye n’ugushira mwo ubushobozi mubihimba vy’imibiri yabo, dushatse twoshobora kuzana abandi bantu atari bo bameze nkabo"
  76,29,"Mu vy’ukuri iki n’icibutso, rero kuwushaka azofata inzira imushikana ku Muremyi wiwe"
  76,30,"Kandi ntimushobora gushaka icarico cose Imana itabishatse, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  76,31,"Yinjiza uwo yishakiye mu migisha yayo, naba hemukiye imitima yabo yarabateguriye ibihano bibabaza cane"